Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:26.67,OP_CN_EP13,,0,1300,0,,{\fs45\fad(220,220)\3c&HE8C854&\bord2\blur10}Whoa-oh-oh-oh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.71,OP_CN_EP13,,0,1300,0,,{\fs45\fad(220,220)\blur1}Whoa-oh-oh-oh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:38.97,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H337BDD&\bord2\blur10}心聲始終緊閉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.18,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H337BDD&\bord2\blur10}淚水幾近決堤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:44.23,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H3C9C6E&\bord2\blur10}迷失於喧囂 沉溺於內心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.10,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H328FC4&\bord2\blur10}但我不會崩潰 絕不迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.23,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H328FC4&\bord2\blur10}故而再度奮起 尋回自我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.94,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H9D49B9&\bord2\blur10}我曾追尋著只屬於我的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.36,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&HE8C854&\bord2\blur10}縱使面對數不盡的絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.86,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H337BDD&\bord2\blur10}縱使理想已然崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:03.41,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H3C9C6E&\bord2\blur10}唯有一把勇氣在手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.04,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H3C9C6E&\bord2\blur10}信念者們 回歸吧 回歸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.38,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H3C9C6E&\bord2\blur10}縱有成千上萬的苦難也不會畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:14.09,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&HE8C854&\bord2\blur10}只因你在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.17,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&HE8C854&\bord2\blur10}我將回歸 回歸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.51,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H3C9C6E&\bord2\blur10}解放吧 無論面對怎樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:24.39,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H3C9C6E&\bord2\blur10}跨越一切 前進吧 挑戰自我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:30.65,OP_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\3c&H9D49B9&\bord2\blur10}跨越一切 前進吧 挑戰自我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.52,OP_CN_EP13,,0,1300,0,,{\fs45\fad(220,220)\3c&H9D49B9&\bord2\blur10}Whoa-oh-oh-oh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.61,OP_CN_EP13,,0,1300,0,,{\fs45\fad(220,220)\3c&H328FC4&\bord2\blur10}Whoa-oh-oh-oh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:40.67,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}光が届かない場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:49.17,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}ひとり何か探していたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:57.18,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}杖を握るその強さは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:03.18,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}僕に少しもなかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:07.19,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}遠くで声が響く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.19,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}届かない夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:15.20,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}僕が僕である限り　終わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:22.53,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}前を向いて歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:31.21,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}悲しみを超えてその向こう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:37.22,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}怯えながら剣で織り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:44.33,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}影の中でも希望信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:52.77,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}この場所で未来を変えていくから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:52.77,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2\fscx60\fscy60\pos(909,1020)}あす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:09.02,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}傷だらけの僕に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:17.26,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}そのままでいいと言ってくれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:25.27,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}震えていたこの掌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:31.27,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}誰か救えると夢見て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:35.28,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}涙がこぼれるたび
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.28,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}増えていく誓い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.23,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}例え届かなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.67,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}限りなく手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:50.77,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}満ちていく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:59.97,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}選ばれし杖の輝き
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:05.07,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}憧れでは終われはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:12.61,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}踏みとどまった昨日の自分を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:20.77,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}変えて明日への道を灯すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:38.69,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}閉ざされた一縷の望みでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:43.05,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}君となら掴める
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:50.59,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}僕を照らしている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:59.36,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}悲しみを超えてその向こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:04.72,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}在る光も　掴んだ力も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:12.60,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}夜を越えれば　新しい朝が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:20.85,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}この場所にきっと訪れるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:28.97,ED_JP_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,0)\blur2}何度でも立ち上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:40.67,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}在光照不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:49.17,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我独自寻觅着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:57.18,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}持杖所需的那份坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:03.18,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我从未拥有一分一毫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:07.19,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}远方回响着呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.19,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}遥不可及的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:15.20,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只要我还是我 便不会终结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:22.53,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}朝着前方迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:31.21,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}跨越悲伤 向着彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:37.22,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}心怀胆怯 以剑织路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:44.33,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}即便身陷暗影也坚信希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:52.77,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}因为我将在此处改写明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:09.02,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}对着满身伤痕的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:17.26,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你说这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:25.27,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}这颤抖的手掌心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:31.27,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}梦想着能拯救某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:35.28,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}每一次泪水滑落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.28,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}誓言便随之增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.23,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}即使无法抵达那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.67,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我也会尽可能地伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:50.77,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}直至圆满
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:59.97,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}选中之杖 绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:05.07,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}憧憬向往 绝不止步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:12.61,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}改变昨日止步不前的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:20.77,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}照亮明日前行的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:38.69,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}哪怕仅是一缕被封存的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:43.05,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}与你一起便能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:50.59,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}将我照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:59.36,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}跨越悲伤 向着彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:04.72,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}拥抱光芒 紧握力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:12.60,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只要熬过漫漫长夜 崭新的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:20.85,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}一定会降临于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:28.97,ED_CN_EP16,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,0)\blur2}无论多少次我都会再站起来
